## Naming Conventions

|Element                                |Convention                               |Example                                                           |
|---------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------|
|Table names                            |`Prefix_Pascal_Snake`                    |`Dim_Employee`, `Fact_Job_Execution`                              |
|Column names                           |`Pascal_Snake`                           |`Queue_Created_Dt`, `Engine_Runtime_Seconds`                      |
|Surrogate keys                         |`[Entity]_Id` (INT IDENTITY)             |`Employee_Id`, `Application_Id`                                   |
|Natural keys (no collision)            |Original source name                     |`Elid`, `Service_Id`                                              |
|Natural keys (collision with surrogate)|`Gallery_[Entity]_Id` or source-qualified|`Gallery_Collection_Id`, `Gallery_Schedule_Id`                    |
|Foreign keys                           |Match the parent surrogate name          |`Employee_Id` on `Fact_Job_Execution` → `Dim_Employee.Employee_Id`|
|Boolean flags                          |`[Noun]_Flag` (BIT)                      |`Error_Flag`, `Change_Champion_Flag`, `Peak_Window_Flag`          |
|Dates (day precision)                  |`[Noun]_Date` (DATE)                     |`Created_Date`, `Termination_Date`                                |
|Timestamps                             |`[Noun]_Dt` (DATETIME2(0))               |`Queue_Created_Dt`, `Completion_Dt`                               |
|Durations                              |`[Noun]_Seconds` (INT)                   |`Engine_Runtime_Seconds`, `Queue_Wait_Seconds`                    |
|Counts                                 |`[Noun]_Count` (INT)                     |`Total_Run_Count`, `Login_Count_Last_90_Days`                     |

