## Adoption Segmentation Reference

These segments are computed in the DAX/BI layer using attributes from `Dim_Employee` and aggregations from `Fact_Job_Execution`. They are point-in-time snapshots, not time series.

|Segment            |Definition                                                   |Source Columns                                                                                      |
|-------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|**License Holder** |Has a desktop Designer license                               |`Dim_Employee.Desktop_License_Flag = 1`                                                             |
|**Server User**    |Has a Gallery account                                        |`Dim_Employee.Server_Account_Flag = 1`                                                              |
|**Change Champion**|Designated to publish to production                          |`Dim_Employee.Change_Champion_Flag = 1`                                                             |
|**Active User**    |Has executed at least one job in the current reporting period|`Fact_Job_Execution` joined to `Dim_Employee`, filtered to current period                           |
|**Orphaned Risk**  |Has server activity but is no longer an employee             |`Dim_Employee.Terminated_Flag = 1` AND exists in `Fact_Job_Execution`                               |
|**Disengaged**     |Active employee with server account but zero flows           |`Dim_Employee.Terminated_Flag = 0` AND `Server_Account_Flag = 1` AND no rows in `Fact_Job_Execution`|
|**At-Risk**        |Active employee, 12+ months since last server access         |`Dim_Employee.Terminated_Flag = 0` AND `Last_Login_Date` < TODAY() − 365                            |

