## Section 3 — Initial Load from Direct_Report.*

**Dependency order (must load in this sequence):**

1. `Dim_Date`
1. `Dim_Employee` (no FKs)
1. `Dim_User_Group` (no FKs)
1. `Dim_Data_Connection` (no FKs)
